#junedump My best month in this city since my Greencard even having a lot of anxiety and allergy crisis with a mix of TMJ syndrome. I met long  time friends and I made new ones. I’ve been working in events since the industry is kind of slow and unpredictable but even so I got 4 call backs, 3 avails and 2 bookings this month. Thank you so much all my reps including my beautiful manager @heather.a.bragg  bc I’m getting too busy and not self submitting to anything. Also I’m not self-taping to every audition I get… and I got one that was huge money 🤷🏻‍♀️😓😓 but I learned with the kind and amazing @ericasbreamcast that it’s ok to say no. We have to respect our limits too. Our future selves will be proud of us. #bekindtoyourself ❤️👐. #actorslife
